## Why This Is Asked
Gauges ability to operationalize privacy across multiple squads and regions while preserving velocity, balancing governance with execution.

## Key Concepts
- Privacy-by-design and DPIA governance
- Data minimization and consent management
- CI gates and artifact templates
- Region-specific privacy budgets and rituals

## Code Example
